text: #Libra I like spending time alone. Just listening to music and thinking.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra “If I ever disrespected you, I meant that, cause I know I let you slide 500 times before I did you like that.”
author: Libras_Society

text:
#Libra One thing about me... 
I notice weird vibes, bad energy and sneaky stuff.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra I hate arguing because I know once I open my mouth, I’ll lose control.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra In a battle between brain and heart, I always listen to my stomach.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra Naturally Introverted, Selectively Extroverted
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra Your next chapter is going to make some people wish they had treated you better.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra I have no capacity of hate in me. It’s either all love or I don’t care.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra “I can make time.” - a love language.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra I’m attracted to mindsets.  Looks ain’t enough, I need to see how you think.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra “Do I actually like you or do I like the romanticized version of you I created in my head.”
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra My biggest toxic trait is I know how to love but I don’t know how to believe I’m loved.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra I am a very forgiving person so if I stop talking to you, you really went too far.
author: Libras_Society

text:
#Libra “People like me don’t have people. We are the people that people have.” 
Read that again
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra One thing about me, I’m cold hearted once trust is gone.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra Humble as ever, but aware of my value.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra Trust issues so bad I don’t even trust the mute button on call.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra One thing i’ll never regret is spending money on food.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra my silence means I’m tired of everything.
author: Libras_Society

text: #Libra I think I’m the nicest rudest most caring nonchalant idgaf person you’ll ever meet.
author: Libras_Society
